---
source: crates/aozora-cli/tests/snapshot_cli.rs
expression: "run(&[\"check\", \"--help\"])"
---
Run the lexer over a file and report diagnostics

Usage: aozora check [OPTIONS] [FILE]

Arguments:
  [FILE]  Input path; pass `-` (or omit) to read from stdin [default: -]

Options:
  -s, --strict               Exit non-zero on any diagnostic
  -E, --encoding <ENCODING>  Source encoding [default: utf8] [possible values: utf8, sjis]
  -h, --help                 Print help
  -V, --version              Print version
